sequenceDiagram
    participant Producer
    participant Mailbox
    participant Consumer
    Producer->>Mailbox: send(msg)
    Mailbox->>Mailbox: queue.size < max?
    alt 容量充足
        Mailbox-->>Producer: ✓ OK
        Consumer->>Mailbox: receive()
    else 容量满
        Mailbox-->>Producer: ✗ BackpressureError
        Producer->>Producer: 等待重试
    end
